import React from 'react'


const SellSVG = (props) => {
    const maskGradient = 'create_gradient-' + props.id
    const maskCharacter = 'create_character-' + props.id

    return (
        <>
            <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 282.22 282.22">
                <defs>
                    <clipPath id={maskGradient}>
                        <circle cx="139.81" cy="138.41" r="107.24" fill="#eb25d2"
                                strokeWidth=".34592"/>
                    </clipPath>
                    <clipPath id={maskCharacter}>
                        <path
                            d="m180.03 0.011271h-91.349v45.369c-33.651 18.64-56.432 54.511-56.432 95.702 0 60.382 48.952 109.33 109.34 109.33 60.385 0 109.34-48.949 109.34-109.33 0-46.853-29.473-86.823-70.892-102.38z"
                            strokeWidth=".35269"/>
                    </clipPath>
                </defs>
                <image transform="matrix(1.0204 0 0 1.0204 -1.1926 -.10558)" x="-.0011139"
                       y="-.0011139" width="282.22"
                       height="282.22" clipPath={`url(#${maskGradient})`} preserveAspectRatio="none"
                       href={props.img_src_create_gradient}/>
                <image x="-.0011139" y="-.0011139" width="282.22" height="282.22"
                       preserveAspectRatio="none"
                       href={props.img_src_shadow}/>
                <image x="-.02335" y="1.0413" width="282.22" height="282.22"
                       clipPath={`url(#${maskCharacter})`} preserveAspectRatio="none"
                       href={props.img_src_create_character}/>
            </svg>
        </>
    )
}

SellSVG.defaultProps = {
    img_src_create_character: '/playground_assets/create_character.png',
    img_src_create_gradient: '/playground_assets/create_gradient.png',
    img_src_shadow: '/playground_assets/ring_shadow.png',

}

export default SellSVG
